snippet.textDisplay: Hi, I am a 54 year old obese dark skin woman. About seven years ago my vitamin D was down to four, they couldn’t understand how I was still standing I’ve been taking vitamin D every since then. Prior to taking the vitamin D I was constantly sick. Since I’ve been taking vitamin D for the last seven years I haven’t had a cold sniffles or nothing I get my flu shot every year and because I had pneumonia in both my lungs back in 07 they gave me the pneumonia shot as well. I think God and vitamin D
